#~ "create a playlist containing the selection of tracks you want, in the "
#~ "<emphasis>Playlist pane</emphasis>. This is where you play your music, "
#~ "streams, or podcasts. You can sort your playlist by title, album, artist, "
#~ "genre and many others. For instance you can sort your tracks by year "
#~ "first, then by artist and so on."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Efter att ha skapat en musiksamling, vill du lyssna på den. Skapa alltså "
